his photographic adventure with a unique visual experience.<br>Explore environments recreated with over 15000 pictures of plants, insects and real animals maded in nature reserves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/41cb5ec13ad304dd4aa063b41149bba9.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/41cb5ec13ad304dd4aa063b41149bba9.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/41cb5ec13ad304dd4aa063b41149bba9.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/fe3216f575e518107b3fe5576ca8b1c7.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/fe3216f575e518107b3fe5576ca8b1c7.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/fe3216f575e518107b3fe5576ca8b1c7.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONTEMPLATE</strong></h2>Change the speed of time and enjoy the view. Contemplate natural life and all its beauty in slow motion. Big Earth is a visual experience like nothing you've experienced before. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/8ddcc24ea38e0c6240714bb67c438ea0.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/8ddcc24ea38e0c6240714bb67c438ea0.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/8ddcc24ea38e0c6240714bb67c438ea0.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/0b41018f1599d46f193f8ca8b659e628.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/0b41018f1599d46f193f8ca8b659e628.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/0b41018f1599d46f193f8ca8b659e628.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PUZZLES</strong></h2>Its intricate puzzles lead the thinking, creativity and skills necessary to solve various challenges on the journey through jungles, forests and dunes. Solve challenging puzzles using seeds and energy capsules. Look for the resources that can be used for the recovery of the planet. Find the equipment that will grow you back to a normal size.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/6a632f3d48c71c2f4e1c3181a45b5036.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/6a632f3d48c71c2f4e1c3181a45b5036.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/6a632f3d48c71c2f4e1c3181a45b5036.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b07613bc98ef5ca0234f699db078f183.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b07613bc98ef5ca0234f699db078f183.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b07613bc98ef5ca0234f699db078f183.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PUZZLE-PLATFORMER</strong></h2>Big Earth's intricate puzzles will challenge your creativity and skills. Solve them by using the seeds and energy capsules collected along your way. Jump, dash, change the speed of time, plant your platforms, and don't forget: nature is always on your side (even when it doesn't look like it). Keep an eye open for the resources that will recover the planet and the equipment capable of restoring you to your standard size. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/91196974a451789d2b35008cdc47f7dc.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/91196974a451789d2b35008cdc47f7dc.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/91196974a451789d2b35008cdc47f7dc.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b4e05ae1cc41ec90cc370afb4e0b7e45.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b4e05ae1cc41ec90cc370afb4e0b7e45.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b4e05ae1cc41ec90cc370afb4e0b7e45.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HEAD UP DISPLAY</strong></h2>Hide the HUD to take photographs and collect memories of the journey. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/f2f82d20847207add0e4b176b09f1ece.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/f2f82d20847207add0e4b176b09f1ece.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/f2f82d20847207add0e4b176b09f1ece.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK</strong></h2>Dr Kyle Seed's mesmerising journey is wrapped in an contemplative original soundtrack that transports the player to a relaxing and challenging environment and sets the mood to the adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b68d5c4edc041c66346fb5bc106d8862.poster.avif?t=1655971431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b68d5c4edc041c66346fb5bc106d8862.webm?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612100/extras/b68d5c4edc041c66346fb5bc106d8862.mp4?t=1655971431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"